Features
  Keyboard Filters
    Shift+Space does underscore '_'
    Home and End do Ctrl-A (beginning-of-line) and Ctrl-E (end-of-line)
    Ctrl-PgUp and Ctrl-PgDn do Home and End
    Right side Command and Alt changed do Ctrl-A and Ctrl-E
    Right side Shift does forward-delete if you release it without pressing another key
    Shift-delete does forward-delete